                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">City police-sergeant,</hi> 93). I got these from Sanderson, and gave them to Nagle.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18500708-name-175" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18500708-name-175" type="gender" value="indeterminate"></interp>
