                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">City-policeman,</hi> 720). I got these from the sergeant, and gave them to Sanderson—I have another bad sixpence, which I found on the prisoner in searching him—I also found on him a shilling, a sixpence, and twelve pence in copper, which were good.</p>
